    <note type="biography">
        <p>Scottish gardener and horticulturist. Gardener to John Campbell, second marquess of Breadalbane, at Taymouth Castle; to Thomas Baring, Strathan Park, Hampshire; to Prince Leopold of Belgium at Claremont, Esher, Surrey; to Walter Francis Scott, fifth duke of Buccleuch, Dalkeith Palace. Author of <hi rend="italic">The book of the garden</hi> (1853–5).</p></note>
